      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、実は芽衣ね～\n今度雑誌の企画に参加することになったの！",
      "startTime": 16,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』\nっていうんだけどね",
      "startTime": 21.4801588817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "お誕生日プレゼントのかわりに\nアイドルがやってみたいことを叶えちゃおう",
      "startTime": 25.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "っていうバースデー企画なんだって！\nもう、今から楽しみだよ～！",
      "startTime": 31.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "わ～！　やってみたいことを叶えてくれるなんて\n素敵な企画ですね。いいな～",
      "startTime": 40.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　すみれちゃんも一緒に参加しない？",
      "startTime": 44.0157828171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　私もですか？",
      "startTime": 47.5924493472,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　さっきの打ち合わせで\n他に二人参加出来ることになったんだ～！",
      "startTime": 52.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_51_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "仲良しなメンバーと一緒の方が、華やかになるし\n企画も盛り上がりそうだから～って！　どうかな？",
      "startTime": 59.8911695692,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
